chließenden Umgang mit Fremdheit im Kontext von Behinderung.  aInclusion as an ideology? This book shows the downsides of the idea of educational inclusion and opens the debate about possible alternatives when dealing with disabilities.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 02. Mrz 2022) 0aEquality. 0aKnowledge, Theory of. 0aMarginality, Social. 0aOther (Philosophy) 0aPeople with disabilities 0aSocial integration. 0aSocial isolation. 4aBehinderung. 4aBernhard Waldenfels. 4aBildung. 4aBildungspolitik. 4aBildungstheorie. 4aFremdheit. 4aHeil- und Sonderpädagogik. 4aInklusionspädagogik. 4aKörper. 4aPädagogik. 4aSoziale Ungleichheit. 7aEDUCATION / Philosophy, Theory & Social Aspects.2bisacsh  aBernhard Waldenfels.  aBody.  aDisability Studies.  aEducation.  aEducational Policy.  aForeignness.  aInclusive Education.  aPedagogy.  aSocial Inequality.  aSpecial Education.  aTheory of Education.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus PP Package 2018 Part 2z978311076667708iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2018z978311071955008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2018z9783110603255oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Social Sciences 2018z9783110603231oZDB-23-DSW40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783839442883zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839442883423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783839442883/original  a978-3-11-071955-0  DG Plus eBook-Package 2018b2018  a978-3-11-076667-7  DG Plus PP Package 2018 Part 2b2018  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_SN  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGGb2017  aZDB-23-DSWb2018